'''Caluula City''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Caluula/Legends|Caluula]]. It was surrounded by rough [[Mountain/Legends|mountains]] on three sides. It was rather low-tech; its streets were largely unpaved and it had a single [[Spaceport/Legends|starport]] that was made out of stone structures. After the [[Battle of Caluula]], the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] placed a [[yammosk]] in the city's center.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

